<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1436,152,698]" pageId="5" pageNumber="14">
Condition of 
<typeStatus box="[354,461,432,458]" pageId="5" pageNumber="14">holotype</typeStatus>
: Moderate, generally dirty. Head greasy, silvery mystical setae gummed up. Antennae lacking postpedicels. Thorax badly cracked down centre of mesonotum, probably the result of a large accumulation of verdigris around the pin within the thoracic cavity. Left hind leg missing beyond trochanter.
</paragraph>
